src:
Dudu cassado (nas redes)

04 Nov 2019, 07:03

Os tuiteiros querem que o mandato de Eduardo Bolsonaro seja cassado.
Segundo a consultoria Levels, citada pela Veja, 66% dos usuários que publicaram mensagens sobre o AI-5 bolsonarista pediram sua degola. Apenas 30% o defenderam.
text:
Dudu Cassado (in the networks)

04 Nov 2019, 07:03

The tweeters want Eduardo Bolsonaro's term to be overturned.
According to the consultancy Levels, cited by Veja, 66% of users who posted messages about the AI-5 scholarship requested their sticking. Only 30% defended him.
